term_description:
The Camden A

The beautiful Camden floor plan is perfect for living and entertaining! A stately foyer as you enter the home opens the formal dining room and to a huge living room with glistening hardwoods and a cozy fireplace. French doors open onto a screened porch for a wonderful outdoor living experience. The gourmet kitchen includes an island, granite counter tops, a large pantry and plenty of room to for more than one chef in the family! The downstairs owner's suite is pure luxury with his and hers walk in closets, granite vanities, a relaxing garden tub, separate shower and water closet. Upstairs has it's own living room along with three large bedrooms and two full baths. This home is a must see!
